<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:1:60">
	The Women’s Auxiliary supports financially, physically and spiritually, the various services of The Salvation Army including the Center of Hope shelter for women and children; area Youth Programs; Christmas assistance programs; the Adult Rehabilitation Center; and more.
</p>
<div class="my-4" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-md:2:73"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:3:90">The greatest need right now is donations for local programs</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:4:52"><a href="https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/give/623102/#!/donation/checkout" class="btn btn-primary gap-1 mt-2">Donate</a></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:5:86"></div>
<div class="row g-3 my-3 align-items-stretch" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:10:74">
