<h5>Scholarships</h5>

<p>
	Provides scholarships for young adults, from The Salvation Army Youth Programs, so they may further their education. <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUYy6pjJVVy_PeEmMwsVwGDjANIbKqI-c" target="">Hear from previous scholarship winners</a>.
</p></div>
				</div>
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 d-flex flex-column" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:10:74-1:2 Columns - Equal:1">
<div class="card-wysiwyg-body d-flex flex-column h-100 w-100 flex-fill rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-area text-dark" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:8:18"><h5><img class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/a1207d63-58dc-4249-ace2-c5fffb2d9b71_food+tray+2.png"></h5>

<h5>Service Activities</h5>

<p>
	Members of the Auxiliary volunteer their time and resources to provide support for families at our Center of Hope who are experiencing homelessness, students at our Salvation Army Youth Programs, participants in the Belmont Community Worship Center senior program, and the men residing at our Adult Rehabilitation Center.
</p></div>
				</div>
			</div>
